{"tid":1723782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動] 出去之前求下大家讀熟地圖","createTime":"2019-11-15T09:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T09:39:36.000Z","uid":28538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cf49dc64acf541bcca3e2e91463b3253403853a1","tid":1723782,"uid":28538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:33:13.000Z","msg":"呢幾日玩香城online<br />\n其實開始注意到個問題並唔係哨兵到 係大家都唔知道哨兵報嘅地方<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係邊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如去中環 <br />\n哨兵: 啲狗係吉野家落地<br />\n夢遊人士: 吉野家喺邊？<br />\n<br />\n你連啲曱甴係邊到唔知邊 落單嘅機會就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">提高</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n解決方法:<br />\n出去之前讀下啲google map，咩街有咩標誌性商舖 呢樣嘢大大提高生存機率！最起碼都讀熟主要道路叫咩街名，唔想再見啲手足太遲行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不鼓吹犯法行為</span>"},{"pid":"573d1d7a324b897d1ef3bdb277077328d4ddfc7c","tid":1723782,"uid":28538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:33:25.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"f4d2d06c3adbb6dbb589e336267b6a94b8ece77d","tid":1723782,"uid":28538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"0e671cc98c63e237650fb6c1469a53a837973126","tid":1723782,"uid":28538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:33:47.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"6b32de7f9ae41464b3e8bc7edd9612640cef2d61","tid":1723782,"uid":28538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:33:59.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"90533005d6b5186aee3a5bcfe84a3f4afeead6df","tid":1723782,"uid":28538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:34:09.000Z","msg":"，"},{"pid":"0627ba11c6d81a0cf396809ea04fbf703e78f69b","tid":1723782,"uid":28538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:34:20.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"5f5cf63d4fbeaeaa4b84a4484629f49a212499de","tid":1723782